Junk Mail
https://botsin.space/@junkmail

This bot keeps track of items present in an Internet Archive collection.
Whenever it posts, it will choose a random page from a random item in that
collection, and fetch it as an image.

$ ia configure
$ botfriend.post --config=bots.sample --bot=junkmail

The posts will show up in bots.sample/junkmail/junkmail.txt
